Package org.ldaptive.schema

Class DITContentRule

java.lang.Object
org.ldaptive.AbstractFreezable
org.ldaptive.schema.AbstractSchemaElement<T>
org.ldaptive.schema.AbstractNamedSchemaElement<String>
org.ldaptive.schema.DITContentRule
All Implemented Interfaces:
Freezable, NamedElement, SchemaElement<String>
public final class DITContentRule extends AbstractNamedSchemaElement<String>
Bean for a DIT content rule schema element. 
   DITContentRuleDescription = LPAREN WSP
     numericoid                 ; object identifier
     [ SP "NAME" SP qdescrs ]   ; short names (descriptors)
     [ SP "DESC" SP qdstring ]  ; description
     [ SP "OBSOLETE" ]          ; not active
     [ SP "AUX" SP oids ]       ; auxiliary object classes
     [ SP "MUST" SP oids ]      ; attribute types
     [ SP "MAY" SP oids ]       ; attribute types
     [ SP "NOT" SP oids ]       ; attribute types
     extensions WSP RPAREN      ; extensions
